show.title: Spark my fire
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/cvMree
show.description: Outside a grand skyscraper, in front of a powerful CEO’s office, a few beautiful girls stand silently in line. Each one has the same hope in her eyes — to be chosen today. This isn't a job — it’s a special contract. The CEO will choose his submissive, a girl who will obey his every command and become a part of his world. The game of money, power, and control is about to begin. Beyond those doors lies a new life — one filled with luxury and grandeur, but only for the one girl… who will live by his rules.
